[normal]A
[normal]s a consequence of the experiences of what
[normal] we do we want to persuade Parliament that it is no longer appropriate that the BBC 
[normal]nor anyone else 
[normal]is funded by an enforced 
[normal]broadcast receiving
[normal] licence regime.  That there must no longer be any criminal or
[normal] civil sanction used against people who cannot afford to or do not want to fund the BBC.  Bring a permanent end of 
[normal]the by 
