[normal]operators
[normal] who are in state of permanent n
[normal]etwork and structural changes.  If private media businesses can do all of th
[normal]ese
[normal] structural strategic 
[normal]things 
[normal]s
[normal]uccessfully 
[normal]and still operate as viable businesses
[normal] then so can the BBC. 
